Fund Investment Objectives











                                        The Arcus Zensen Fund aims to provide positive returns through investment in long and short exposures in Japanese equities. The criteria used to evaluate stocks include the companies' earnings generation, future potential earnings growth and actual and potential asset value. AUM combines both currency classes and is in USD. 
                                    

















 




















